{"tid":1130315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"擴大施壓馬杜洛政權 美宣布制裁委內瑞拉外長","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T03:03:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"984d2af01aa30922295800646835ecbeb554005b","tid":1130315,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"擴大施壓馬杜洛政權 美宣布制裁委內瑞拉外長<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E6%B4%9B%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7-200502263.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25A3%2593%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259D%259C%25E6%25B4%259B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E5%2588%25B6%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2591%259E%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2595%25B7-200502263.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9d7g8jx8mLjpq94TYZylSB8%3D&h=629747b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%BD%E5%A3%93%E9%A6%AC%E6%9D%9C%E6%B4%9B%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A-%E7%BE%8E%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81%E5%A7%94%E5%85%A7%E7%91%9E%E6%8B%89%E5%A4%96%E9%95%B7-200502263.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（法新社華盛頓26日電） 美國擴大施壓欲將委內瑞拉總統馬杜洛（Nicolas Maduro）拉下台，今天宣布對委國外交部長阿雷亞薩（Jorge Arreaza）施以制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國財政部長梅努欽（Steven Mnuchin）今天聲明：「對於非法的馬杜洛政權剝奪委內瑞拉人民財富、人道和民主權利，美國不會袖手旁觀。」他同時宣布封鎖阿雷亞薩在美國的任何資產。<br />\n<br />\n為尋求扶正反對派領袖瓜伊多（Juan Guaido）為委國總統，這項制裁是美國對委國高層最新的打擊動作。<br />\n<br />\n儘管之前的大多制裁都是指官員貪腐或違反權利，但美國財政部今天卻未援引特定違反項目，而是依阿雷亞薩的外長角色施以制裁。<br />\n<br />\n阿雷亞薩在推特做出回應，將制裁與他前一天前往聯合國訪問時對抗美國「有罪的封鎖」委內瑞拉相互連結，並說他所聽到的反應顯示「我們所走的路是正確方向」。<br />\n<br />\n自1月美國和多數拉丁美洲國家宣布馬杜洛為非法政權以來，新聞記者出身的阿雷亞薩已數度前往紐約，代表委國在聯合國發聲。（譯者：徐睿承）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FsduUjHbTJ4z0MVfy7Ziaw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDQw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/afp.cnanews.gov.tw/9517612dcc024d422d4d5c09fc4621b9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FFsduUjHbTJ4z0MVfy7Ziaw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjMwO2g9NDQw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fafp.cnanews.gov.tw%2F9517612dcc024d422d4d5c09fc4621b9&h=a35d3f53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b5cc74742d911f28b41e76fbe6eb2e22492d08d","tid":1130315,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"俄軍已登陸"}]}